data.description: NEWLY RENOVATED Bright, spacious home tucked into this quiet, friendly S. Waldo neighborhood near parks, schools, shopping, convenience stores & great local restaurants! Newly landscaped garden beds line the steps up to the door of your freshly updated new home. Just inside the front door lies new luxury vinyl plank waterproof flooring, fresh new carpeting with upgraded luxury padding, all new interior interior paint and trim. The formal living room has a beautiful new deep green colored geometric accent wall. The heart of the home - the kitchen, dining and family room have recently been updated with new granite countertops, newly painted cabinets carrying that green, nature inspired hue. Stainless steel appliances all stay with the home. Take advantage of the walk-in pantry plus plenty of cabinet storage as well. Take a step out back and enjoy your private, fully-fenced backyard oasis, ready for relaxing or entertaining. Enjoy the HUGE master bedroom retreat with new ceiling fan, hardwood floors, lots of natural light & plenty of closet space! The 2nd main floor bedroom features a new ceiling fan, fresh new paint & doors. In the basement, you'll find a fresh new bedroom and ensuite bathroom, plus a large, versatile rec room, perfect for movie nights, a play room, or a private office! Everything has been done for you here, all that's missing is you! Seller is Agent/Owner.
